        <p>January 11, 2019</p>
			
        <p>Python is a programming language that lets you work more
        quickly and integrate your systems more effectively. You
        can learn to use Python and see almost immediate gains in
        productivity and lower maintenance costs.</p>

        <h2>Python Links</h2>

        <p>More information can be found at
        <a href="http://www.python.org/">this website</a>.</p>

        <h2>ElectricFlow Integration to Python</h2>

        <p>The EC-Python plugin allows you to run any Python script
        by writing it directly in the script area provided or
        provide the path to any python file.</p>

        <p>The plugin also allows you to review the log that
        contains output and errors resulting from execution, just
        as the Python compiler does.</p>

        <h2>Integrated Version</h2>

        <p>This plugin was developed and tested against version
        2.7.2.</p>

